'''二草酸根合硼酸锂'''是一种化合物，化学式为LiB(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>，它可用于锂离子电池中。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Electrochemical and Solid-State Letters|volume=5|issue=1|language=en|date=2002|pages=A26|doi=10.1149/1.1426042|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1149/1.1426042|title=LiBOB as Salt for Lithium-Ion Batteries:A Possible Solution for High Temperature Operation|accessdate=2020-11-20|author=Kang Xu, Shengshui Zhang, T. Richard Jow, Wu Xu, C. Austen Angell}}</ref>

==制备与反应==

二草酸根合硼酸锂可由[[草酸|草酸]]、[[氢氧化锂|氢氧化锂]]和[[硼酸|硼酸]]加热反应制得：<ref name=Yu>{{cite journal|journal=Electrochemical and Solid-State Letters|volume=9|issue=1|language=en|date=2006|pages=A1|doi=10.1149/1.2128122|url=https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1149/1.2128122|title=The Electrochemical Characterization of Lithium Bis(oxalato)borate Synthesized by a Novel Method|accessdate=2020-11-20|author=Bi-Tao Yu, Wei-Hua Qiu, Fu-Shen Li, Guo-Xiang Xu}}</ref>
: 2 H<sub>2</sub>C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>·2H<sub>2</sub>O + LiOH·H<sub>2</sub>O + H<sub>3</sub>BO<sub>3</sub> → LiB(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub> + 9 H<sub>2</sub>O

它可以在300 °C以上分解，生成[[碳酸锂|碳酸锂]]：<ref name=Yu />
: 2 LiB(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub> → Li<sub>2</sub>CO<sub>3</sub> + B<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + 4 CO + 3 CO<sub>2</sub>
